{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Summary\u3011</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>What on earth is this school?! </strong></i>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/intro01.png?t=1739772309\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weird encounters happened to Natsumi on the first day of her transference</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Counseling Teacher looking for trouble, the Principal with religious fanaticism, and Classmates with absurd common sense ...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meeting classmates and teachers with unique personalities at the start of the semester, can she get used to school life from now on?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Controls\u3011</strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/intro07.png?t=1739772309\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b2Use arrow keys to control Natsumi and use the Z key to interact with classmates and teachers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b2Use the Mouse wheel to check the Backlog and use the Right click to open the Menu!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/intro04.png?t=1739772309\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b2Attend classes and increase knowledge!<br>Although sometimes it might be a self-study period ...?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3326920/extras/\u87a2\u5e55\u64f7\u53d6\u756b\u9762_2024-11-04_105057.png?t=1739772309\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25b2Because this is an absurd academy, sparring with classmates is a compulsory subject!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea